{"type": "article", "id": 31506, "title": "把旧手机当作魔术道具 | Card2Phone", "description": "", "date": "1970-01-01T00:00:00Z", "super_tag": null, "tags": [], "category": null, "author": 553548, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 1, "image": "img/default_images/missing_article.png", "contents": "<p>表演性的近景魔术，除了要用到一些特制的道具，还可以下载某些精心设计的应用。</p><p>手指灵活，勤加练习的话，你也能营造出专业魔术师的效果。</p><p class=\"\">Card2Phone 就是这样一款以纸牌为主题的魔术道具应用。</p><p class=\"\">它目前只有<a href=\"https://itunes.apple.com/us/app/card2phone-magic-trick/id372047576?mt=8\" rel=\"nofollow\"> iOS 版本</a>，而且需要支付 5 美元才能下载使用。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160902192526EqHW9g71An5z0Ye4.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.882353\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\">Card2Phone 截图</figcaption></figure></div><p class=\"\">至于具体玩法，Card2Phone 会在引导环节告诉你那些小技巧究竟是怎样实现的。</p><p class=\"\">这里有个<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=p9rgn0Z0f74\" rel=\"nofollow\">小视频</a>，展示了用 Card2Phone 变魔术博得欢呼的精彩瞬间。</p><p class=\"\">如果你舍不得用你崭新的 iPhone 练习魔术，不妨给旧手机装上这款应用，熟能生巧，练着练着就学会了。</p>"}